 Group (AUS/FRA)\nKlo 21.00\n\nPerjantai 12.9.\nTonight at Noon (FIN)\nKlo 
 19.00\n\nSam Yahel Trio (USA)\nKlo 21.00\n\nLauantai 13.9.\nTimo Lassy Ban
 d (FIN)\nKlo 19:00\n\nELEW (USA)\nKlo 21.00\n\nwww.porvoojazzfestival.com
