BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Harju 8 Jam session (Jam Park)
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Helsinki:20190630T180000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Helsinki:20190630T210000
DTSTAMP:20260504T185210Z
UID:4eoe4n99ltl87hq7qtb39mvrcl@google.com
SEQUENCE:0
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;COUNT=5;BYDAY=SU;WKST=MO
CREATED:20190625T130947Z
DESCRIPTION:Harju 8\nStarting from 6pm till 9pm.\nstarting from the 30th J
 une and going through every Sundays of July.\nThis is the perfect appointm
 ent for all the jazz musician in Helsinki (straight piano available for al
 l the musicians at the jam and the instrumentations of the opening band). 
 Every time a different trio hosted by Alessandro performing originals and 
 jazz standards of the american tradition.\n\n" Nuoresta iästään huolima
 tta D'Anna on ehtinyt kiertää Eurooppaa sellaisten jazzmuusikoiden kanss
 a kuin David Kikoski\, Benito Gonzalez\, Mark Gross\, Eve Cornelious\, Ben
 ny Benack III\, and many others".\n\n30.06 New Standards Jam feat. Mikko I
 nnanen\nMikko Innane: sax alto\nJuuso Kasperi Rinta: doublebass\nAlessandr
 o D'Anna: drums\n\n7.07 New Standards Jam feat. Max Zenger\nMax Zenger: sa
 x alto and bass clarinet\nTeemu Åkerblom: doublebass\nAlessandro D'Anna: 
 drums\n\n14.07 New Standards Jam feat. Riitta Paakki\nRiitta Paakki: piano
 \nJuuso Kasperi Rinta: doublebass\nAlessandro D'Anna: drums\n\n21.7 New St
 andards Jam feat. Toms Rudzinskis Trio\nToms Rudzinskis: sax alto\nTuomo U
 usitalo: piano\nAlessandro D'Anna: drums\n\n28.7 New Standards Jam feat. M
 anuel Dunkel\nManuel Dunkel: tenor sax\nNathan Francis: doublebass\nAlessa
 ndro D'Anna: drums
LAST-MODIFIED:20190625T130947Z
LOCATION:Harju 8\, Harjutori 8\, 00500 Helsinki\, Suomi
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-JAZZFI-SOURCE:gcal
END:VEVENT
