BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Montenia (USA) with the Wade Mikkola Trio
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Helsinki:20130411T220000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Helsinki:20130411T220000
DTSTAMP:20260504T185211Z
UID:2o1g7encqb5v7203h68mo4p4s0@google.com
SEQUENCE:0
RRULE:FREQ=DAILY;COUNT=3
CREATED:20130407T110207Z
DESCRIPTION:The powerful and soulful vocalist Montenia makes her yearly ap
 pearance at the Storyville on April 11th until 13th. She is accompanied by
  the trio that was on her 1999 CD "Each and Every Day" which was recorded 
 live at the Storyville. The trio consists of Lasse Hirvi on piano (Riitta 
 Paakki on Saturday)\, Tomi Parkkonen on drums\, and\, of course\, Wade on 
 bass.\nThe songs include rarely heard compositions by Abbey Lincoln\, and 
 great standards arranged by Nancy Wilson's pianist Llew Matthews. It will 
 be three grand nights of SWINGING!!!\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20221202T235840Z
LOCATION:Storyville\, Museokatu 8\, Helsinki
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-JAZZFI-SOURCE:gcal
END:VEVENT
