 r koko tapahtuman ajan!\n\nHelsinki based Friction Groove Collective can h
 ave up to a dozen musicians contributing\, and plays a mixture of afrobeat
 \, jazz\, and latin cumbia\, harmoniously blending diverse genres and cult
