 ne Bar.<br><br>Every Friday\, your favorite Georgian corner in Helsinki tr
 ansforms into a soulful jazz spot\, curated by Kalevi ‘Aceman’ Louhivu
 ori.<br><br>This musical journey will take you everywhere from the sun-soa
 ked rhythms of Bossa Nova and heartfelt tributes to Ella Fitzgerald\, to t
 he legendary\, cool chords of Chet Baker. It’s the ultimate blend of jaz
 z\, blues\, and romance.<br><br>24 April – Elina Kardén Trio: Bossa Nov
 a Classics<br>1 May – Harriet Honkaniemi Quartet – Jazz &amp\; Soul Cl
 assics<br>8 May – Anna Inginmaa Trio – Ella Fitzgerald Tribute<br>15 M
