 i. Under the artistic direction of Alessandro D’Anna the new venue hosts
  musicians from all around the world. Busy music program\, amazing italian
  food and wine\, unique cocktail bar\, Officine Brera is a new experience 
 in Helsinki.\n\n23.04. \nRiitta Paakki - piano\nTuomo Purhonen - double b
 ass\nAlessandro D'Anna - drums\n\nReserving your table for the food experi
 ence is highly suggested to support the music\, no ticket fee is requested
 . Main hall is dedicated to the food experience while reservation for the 
